## DM 2 — The Follow-Up (Day 5)
**New angle. Not a nudge. Hard stop after this one.**

---

**Follow-Up A** *(pairs with Variants A, B, or C)*
```
[First Name] — one more thought before I leave you alone.

The coaches who get this early aren't more tech-savvy. They just
stopped waiting to see how it plays out.

