## Response Handling Scripts

### "Yes / Send the link"
```
Here you go: [webinar link]

Tuesday, March 24 — 7 PM ET. Doors open 6:45.
No replay, live only. See you there.
```

### "What's it about?"
```
It's a live training on how coaches are building a team of AI
employees — not tools, actual workers with defined roles — handling
email, content, follow-up, and outreach.

The whole thing runs $39/month. I'll show the full setup live.

March 24, 7 PM ET: [webinar link]
```

### "I already use AI"
```
Good — you'll move faster than most in the room.

This is the step beyond tools. AI employees with roles, workflows,
and actual accountability. Different level of leverage.

March 24: [webinar link]
```

### "AI doesn't work for me"
```
That's exactly the conversation I want to have on March 24.

Most people have been sold tools when what they actually need
is workers. Takes about 15 minutes to see the difference.

[webinar link] if you want to check it out.
```

### "Not interested"
```
No problem — appreciate you responding. Good luck with everything.
```

### No reply after both DMs
Archive. Do not send a third message. If they engage with your content organically in the next 30 days, re-open the conversation with a fresh message. That's the only re-entry point.

