## Volume Tips

- **Run one variant per batch** — don't mix. This lets you see which angle pulls best.
- **Variant B (competition angle) tends to get the most replies** — it creates urgency without pressure.
- **Send DM 1 in the morning** (8-10 AM their timezone if possible). DM 2 on Day 5, same window.
- **Do not change the DM template mid-batch** — give each variant at least 20-30 sends before judging it.
- **Track replies by variant** so you know what to scale.

